  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5466972">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5466972/" class="title-link">不对等的战场</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5466972"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46909885/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u46909885-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46909885/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我就是神</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-15 16:37:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5466972_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书中描写的意大利军队和法军一无是处，而又过分吹嘘英军、澳大利亚等的战斗力。 其实北非根本就是军力完全一个不对等的战场。如果隆美尔有与英军相当的兵力和补给，哪怕给隆美尔提供一个装备IV号战车的装甲师，北非战争必将是倒向德军的。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            北岳文艺出版社1992版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5466972_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5466972_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3549500">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3549500/" class="title-link">昔日之书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3549500"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1182787-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1182787/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">拔刀诀</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-15"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-15 22:11:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3549500_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  同为战史小说，比不上作者的另一部《燃烧的岛群》。 首先书名不是很合适，恰当的该叫北非战记。本书中隆美尔虽是主要演员，但墨索里尼，丘吉尔，罗斯福，蒙哥马利都占了不小的篇幅，尤其是第一章，就是一个墨索里尼小传，没隆美尔什么事。 书中对北非乃至地中海沿岸的地理风俗...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3549500_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3549500_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
